{"tid":1694830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"事到如今，攬炒係唯一出路","createTime":"2019-11-05T10:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:25.000Z","uid":216228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0e86e9478564e6c987aaff97d96f03c0959927","tid":1694830,"uid":216228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:00:34.000Z","msg":"但唔係叫你同啲黑警硬拼。<br />\n每人100條命都唔夠死。<br />\n<br />\n積極擴大黃色經濟圈嘅發展。<br />\n每人行多一步嘅力量真係唔好睇少。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你唔好出嚟抗爭。<br />\n但要識走識避。唔好再送頭。<br />\n唔好企定定，啲狗捉人先走已經太遲。<br />\n做多啲快閃。<br />\n<br />\n武鬥根本無可能會赢。"},{"pid":"9b829e90bd724c67b4b080c691c3a29d264313ab","tid":1694830,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 認輸</span></span>"}]}